Second Department,

(February 4, 1957) Albert C. Eidelberg, Appellant, v. Charlotte Kestenbaum et al., Respondents.

Motion to amend decision and for other relief denied, without costs. Present — -Nolan, P. J., Wenzel, Beldock, Hallinan and Kleinfeld, JJ. [See ante, p. 663.]
